  "imageCount": 6,
  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598755739499-PEPJV4K9WWFLRFWHM285/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Recently I had the pleasure of teaching at a huge store called <a href=\"http://www.hannahs.com/\">Hannah's Home Accents</a> in Antioch, IL. It's always so neat connecting and creating with such awesome people. </p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"20b-20140627-103233-37953762.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598755763541-OSB606HOIVXGTW431OJW/20b-20140627-103233-37953762.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"20c-20140627-103230-37950868.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598755763678-OVNVONKUKMXHLAZ21CXU/20c-20140627-103230-37950868.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20d-20140627-103232-37952976.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598755764253-TKR4JCRFQ05S6RIH2A6A/20d-20140627-103232-37952976.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20e-20140627-103231-37951825.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598755764558-5E1ACL9DOBP21599DC2L/20e-20140627-103231-37951825.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20f-20140627-103232-37952478.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598755764991-8IL1HB0WF4MDBGB0YTYK/20f-20140627-103232-37952478.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Thanks for having me, Dana! And thanks to everyone who joined in as well. You all are awesome and inspired me to sign stuff using watercolors! I'll be making a quick trip up to Berkeley on July 11th (the class sold out in less than 24 hours!) and then take a little break for in person classes until the fall. If there are any leftover kits, I will be sure to blog about it and make them available. Remember, from anywhere around the world, you can still join me for <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=52016&amp;m=9622&amp;afftrack=here%26there&amp;urllink=www%2Ebigpictureclasses%2Ecom%2Fhere%2Dand%2Dthere%2Ephp\">Here &amp; There Inspiration</a> which begins on July 3!</p>"
